# TypeScript Data Validation

## External Data
- ✅ External data must be validated for type
- ✅ Use classes with `class-validator` decorators for raw data validation
- ✅ Use `validateObject` function
- ✅ Validate all inputs before processing

## Data Structures
- ✅ Prefer immutable data structures
- ✅ Use TypeScript interfaces for data contracts
- ✅ Validate data at boundaries (API endpoints, file inputs, etc.)
